::Koj::

Koj Looking at the base "I think we should talk about me later you have a 
friend to rescue and I have a enemy to kill." As the blade sticking out of 
his forehead glows silver and Fires a beam into the air.

::Inu-Yasha::

Inu-Yasha not to far away sees the beam and turns around.

::Koj::

Koj holds up his arm as sparks fly from the damaged limb grabs Inu-Yasha leg 
and swings on to his back. "Lets head towards the Swamp."


::Both::

They both rocket off towards the swamp.
